- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper discusses various libraries for homomorphic encryption and their features for secure computation. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also likely as the paper discusses trade-offs and complexities of different approaches to homomorphic encryption. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper may discuss the data structures and algorithms used in the different libraries. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as homomorphic encryption can be used in secure machine learning applications. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possibility as the paper discusses the support for different languages and real-life applications of the libraries.
